@kallewoof 1. Cure it and turn it into bacon (takes about a week)
2. Put it into the oven for about 8 hours at 110 C or so, seasoned however you like. The leftovers are good for a week or so and great for fried rice, etc.
3. Chop into 5 cm cubes and refreeze what you don't eat.

